{"tid":1562103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家可以主動啲幫跳閘嘅手足","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:15:32.000Z","uid":78701,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c82ba92eb4a76b1074a2db97fb57b9489433e168","tid":1562103,"uid":78701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:24:18.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪因為呢排咁多藍絲捉跳閘片，而家越嚟越多人會出聲叫職員，咁我地冇理由下下都期地鐵職員會係同路人，所以我地一定自救。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，希望啲口才好嘅手足<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>跳閘<br />\n出聲嘅要話自己冇跳閘，唔好俾人spin去冇俾錢就唔啱。<br />\n<br />\n第二，見到有人捉跳閘就行埋去擋cam<br />\n俾人見到跳閘嘅手足就襯而家走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就<span style=\"color: red;\">大大聲</span>問<br />\n &ldquo;<strong>你知唔知佢地點解要跳閘呀</strong>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n以我嘅經驗大部分藍絲呢個時候就會話唔想知就敗走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果佢繼續留低呢?<br />\n<br />\n咁就啱曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁好嘅文宣機會大家要好好把握<br />\n<br />\n記得講得大聲啲務求要經過嘅人都聽到<br />\n同大家宣傳<br />\n-831太子站地鐵冇公開CCTV<br />\n-901用機鐵運警察<br />\n-908封地鐵唔俾示威者走<br />\n-呢個係公民不合作運動<br />\n-極度和平理性非暴力<br />\n大家呢個位可以自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我建議盡量<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好講粗口</span><br />\n因為我地係嚟做公關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣又可以保護手足，又可以廢咗佢條片，仲可以逼經過嘅人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以多啲出口幫堅持跳閘嘅手足，唔好再因為跳閘搞佢地俾人拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1927f67003c5a5ff46c0a7626a470e0db95b945","tid":1562103,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e341e1e2f7dccf514dad145c4b889f6c5b147302","tid":1562103,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73a2bcf28d846cedd8c4a1ae2af8bf2cc634d553","tid":1562103,"uid":205515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"我願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"2331d593b1cc442ce67e2e2b5402b0c3a1d513a9","tid":1562103,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c82ba92eb4a76b1074a2db97fb57b9489433e168","tid":1562103,"uid":78701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:24:18.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪因為呢排咁多藍絲捉跳閘片，而家越嚟越多人會出聲叫職員，咁我地冇理由下下都期地鐵職員會係同路人，所以我地一定自救。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，希望啲口才好嘅手足<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>跳閘<br />\n出聲嘅要話自己冇跳閘，唔好俾人spin去冇俾錢就唔啱。<br />\n<br />\n第二，見到有人捉跳閘就行埋去擋cam<br />\n俾人見到跳閘嘅手足就襯而家走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 